Description: Provides functions to estimate minimal important change and
    interpretation thresholds using anchor-based methods. Methods include
    ROC analysis, predictive modeling, adjusted predictive modeling, improved
    adjusted predictive modeling using anchor reliability, confirmatory factor
    analysis for anchor reliability, longitudinal confirmatory factor analysis
    for minimal important change, and CFA-based thresholds for single-item and
    multi-item measures.
